snippet.textDisplay:
"Muskurate huye qaabe ko Ali yaad aya..." Waah, kya line hain! Jee bhar gaya... I cry, cry and cry with an unexpressible feeling inside me when I listen to Sufi music... I don't know how I started loving Sufi music. Actually, I am wrong. I didn't start loving, Sufi embraced me seeing my thirsty musical Heart. 
"Khud pe haq hai mera,
Socha tha pehle...
Tune raah dikhaya jyon,
Jaan gaya...
Main toh hota hi nahi..."
Love from Assam, India
(Javed is love...)
